43
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:14,720
For those of you who are not, essentially what we have seen is a

44
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:20,030
systematic targeting on the part of the Khartoum government and the

45
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:26,940
