74
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:35,680
primarily providing witness to some of the atrocities that are

75
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,120
taking place there.

76
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,930
But they don't have clear rules of engagement.

77
00:04:39,930 --> 00:04:42,510
And they're under-armed, under-trained.

78
00:04:42,510 --> 00:04:47,140
They don't really provide the sort of protective force that would be needed

